The project also includes a simple graphical launcher:

    python gui_tumor_growth_analysis.py

In the graphical window, you can:

    1: Type or paste the Excel file path.
    2: Click Browse and select the Excel file.
    3: Choose an output folder.
    4: Click Run Analysis.

Drag and drop support is optional and requires tkinterdnd2, which is included in requirements.txt. If drag and drop does not work, the Browse button will still work.